 with personality and vibrancy. The walls are painted in Farrow \u0026amp; Ball’s Strong White, a cool shade with subtle gray undertones, providing a crisp backdrop. Meanwhile, the headboard features Elephant Breath, a warm gray hue that echoes the texture and tone of the fluted bathroom tiles, seamlessly linking the bedroom and bathroom aesthetics.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569665\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569665\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-4-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern art on the wall, gray sofa with black pillow, pink tulips in vase, shelves with books in a bright room.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-4-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-4-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-4-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-4-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-4-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569666\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569666\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-5-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with a white round table, a pink vase, a book with a blue cover, a mid-century wooden chair, and herringbone-patterned wooden floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" 