/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-6-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569668\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569668\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-7-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern room featuring a wooden chair, a bust on a pedestal, contemporary art on the wall, a small table with a pink vase of tulips, and a glimpse into the adjacent bedroom.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-7-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-7-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-7-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-7-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-7-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe thoughtful use of materials further enhances this balance. Brushed stainless steel accents – seen in light switches, door handles, curtain rods, and lighting fixtures – lend a modern edge, while timeless Carrara marble, featured on the coffee table, kitchen countertop, and bathroom tiles, brings a sense of classic luxury. These materials create continuity throughout the apartment, tying together different areas with a sense of understated elegance.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569669\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569669\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-8-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist kitchen with brown and black cabinetry, wood herringbone floor, white walls, cream curtains, and a sculpted bust on a pedestal. A coffee machine and framed artwork sit on the counter.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-8-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-8-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-8-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-8-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-8-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo optimize the compact layout, strategic decisions were made to utilize space efficiently. The kitchen, now positioned near the entrance, features custom cabinetry with IKEA pedestals and \u0026amp;SHUFL fronts in a raw finish – black for the base units and light gray for the upper cabinets. Despite its small footprint, the kitchen is fully equipped with a sink, two burners, an oven, and a fridge, making it both functional and stylish.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569670\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569670\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-9-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist interior with a wooden chair, a wall lamp, and a glimpse of a bedroom with a white bed and curtain drawn back.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-9-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-9-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-9-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-9-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-9-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569671\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569671\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-10-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom with beige cabinetry, a white bed, and patterned pillows. A mirror is mounted on the wall above the headboard.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-10-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-10-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-10-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-10-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-10-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe bedroom was relocated to the former kitchen area, with a custom-designed headboard extending to ceiling height, offering both visual impact and additional storage. A trunk bed by Tediber provides hidden storage, maximizing space without compromising comfort. The bathroom was reconfigured to include a space-saving roller shutter door and a central partition that separates the toilet and shower, maintaining functionality while enhancing privacy. A transparent, reflective glass door ensures that natural light filters into the space, creating an airy feel even in the most compact areas.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569672\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569672\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-11-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bedroom with a white bed, patterned pillows, and beige wall storage. A monochrome artwork is displayed above the bed, with a sleek, modern design.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-11-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-11-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-11-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-11-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-11-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLighting plays a pivotal role in enhancing the perception of space and adding warmth. In the living area, two mirrors were positioned above the shelves to reflect daylight without directing the viewer’s eye toward their own reflection, subtly enlarging and brightening the room. In the bedroom, a mirrored upper section of the headboard amplifies the light, while an artwork by Thomas Devaux, featuring dichroic glass, introduces dynamic reflections that generate their own glow, adding an ethereal dimension to the space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569673\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569673\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-12-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A wall with a framed abstract artwork depicting a blue figure. Below, a black side table holds a stack of books.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-12-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-12-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-12-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-12-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-12-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569674\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569674\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-13-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bedroom with white walls features an open door leading to a bathroom with a round mirror. A colorful painting hangs on the wall, and a black side table with books is beside the bed.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-13-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-13-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-13-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-13-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-13-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569675\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569675\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-14-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with marble tiles, wall-mounted round mirror, rectangular sink, and shower area. Bottles of toiletries are on the sink countertop.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-14-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-14-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-14-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-14-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-14-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569676\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569676\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-15-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with a wall-mounted toilet, a floating rectangular sink, and a round mirror. The walls have a mix of marble and textured tile.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-15-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-15-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-15-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-15-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-15-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=569677\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-569677\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apartment-Emilie-Magdelaine-16-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior with a kitchen featuring black cabinets, a bust on a pedestal, a low cream chair, wooden floors, and large windows with white curtains.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/Bergere-Paris-IX-Apa